Package: githubr
Title: Interface to GitHub from R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Luke", "Johnston", email = "lwjohnst@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4169-2616"))
Description: Based around the gh package, this package provides a user-friendly 
    interface to GitHub. Functions include adding or closing Issues, setting labels, 
    or creating new repositories. Most GitHub API requests are or will be available.
